        "rating": "3", 
        "review": "Actor; director; environmentalist and political activist; Robert Redford possesses one of the world's most recognizable visages, but his well-known reserve has kept his secrets well&#58; Who among us, for instance, can name his long-time lover, now wife? This authorized biography opens the vaults on the very active life of this Hollywood icon. Drawing on journals, correspondence, script notes, and hundreds of hours of taped interviews, biography Michael Feeney reveals the fascinating man behind that handsome face. An unprecedented intimate portrait of a two-time Oscar winner.", 
