        "description": "Alone on the battlefield.Surrounded by death.Cornered by enemies.And ready to die.Drizzt Do&#8217;Urden has become the Hunter, the bane of the orc hordes still ravaging the North. Cut off, alone, convinced that everything he ever valued has been destroyed, all that&#8217;s left is to kill, and kill, and kill, until there are no enemies left. But there are a lot of enemies, and even the Hunter is just one lone drow.", 
