        "rating": "4", 
        "review": "As viewers of herBarefoot Contessashow can attest, Ina Garten favors simple, sophisticated dishes, main courses that evoke the best of cozy bistro meals. InBarefoot in Paris,the Food Network star applies her cooking wisdom to the foods of France. Favoring fresh, quality ingredients, she offers flavorful twists on old favorites such as Steak au Poivre and Cr\u00e8me Brul&eacute;e and new slants on dishes such as Zucchini Vichyssoise and Chicken with Morels. A feast of a book,Barefoot in Pariscontains 140 full-color photographs and a primer for sources for specialty ingredients.", 
