        "description": "For five novels, Clive Cussler has brought readers into the world of theOregon, a seemingly dilapidated ship packed with cutting edge technology and captained by the daring Juan Cabrillo. Now, theOregonand its crew face their biggest challenge yet-with a danger torn from today's headlines...", 
